title: Lauren Taylor & Berelc Mingle With Peyton Meyer at the Mattel Pier Party!
text: Lauren Taylor and Paris Berelc both step out in style for the 2015 Mattel Party On The Pier held at Santa Monica Pier on Sunday (September 27) in Santa Monica, Calif. The young actresses were joined at the bash by Nathan Kress, Francesca Capaldi, August Maturo, Peyton Meyer, Corey Fogelmanis, Veronica Dunne, Chris Brochu, and [...] Â»
